{"tid":303760,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓食份量問題","createTime":"2017-06-30T11:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T18:41:54.000Z","uid":14706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f97d7e639af4996467c864c7682a67454ddfbed2","tid":303760,"uid":14706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"我以前分2餐比佢食, 朝早乾糧~40G左右 夜晚5.5OZ濕糧分三分一加半條雞柳比佢<br />\n<br />\n發覺佢朝早6點幾係咁叫想搵野食, 餵夜晚前1/2個鍾又係咁<br />\n<br />\n咁我以為比唔夠野佢食, 早晚一樣份量再下午加多餐比佢<br />\n<br />\n但情況冇改善到, 想問吓大家係我餵唔夠定佢真係大食到咁?<br />\n<br />\n補充返, 3歲 ~4.5KG"},{"pid":"c13d78c54c93d931ff6cbee300fdb97fa48d3e0b","tid":303760,"uid":14706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94ca990c50e8c86fdf02ce659d68f689471ac16","tid":303760,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:21:11.000Z","msg":"冇圖好難討論落去喎<br />\n唔知品種，唔知重量又唔知Size<br />\n<br />\n利申:其實我想R貓圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b212d284bb2e342582bb373afdb025c5018d4b61","tid":303760,"uid":14706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"求巴打們比D意見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Xxkxul1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXxkxul1.jpg&h=99f02e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lEVl0A0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlEVl0A0.jpg&h=38f14184&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc3b9bb9f4402e3d1ace929f37e8c9532b39ec27","tid":303760,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"我餵長糧佢都會定時喵<br />\n應該唔關事"},{"pid":"3be377f5758298d53026f55cbfb749682ce650f9","tid":303760,"uid":50032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:58: